Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to introduce Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All praise be to thee, O Lord, most high.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, we set the context of reality for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we'll be calibrating all kinds of levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And what these levels mean, it means relative to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So God will be here to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nothing to worry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are we talking about again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me, and I went and forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the secret of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret of life was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the secret of life, we'll get to later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you already know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we'll just remind you that you're only going to be learning what you already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it nice, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, today is, I've declared it to be National Humility Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's our humility?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the person who's the most humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the most humble person in the.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the most humble person to raise their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the humility award for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, today is going to be a very serious day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Humor is, humor is what's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragedy is crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everybody's, everybody's full of tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dime a dozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, uh, what were we talking about again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that sounds scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as we're here and there's a whole audience, we might as well give a lecture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We might as well do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, anybody want me to discuss spiritual challenges?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Two left jabs and a right cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That knocks the devil right on his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have slides that we're going to be talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, there is a method to our madness today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a certain coherent sanity behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Which we won't reveal, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've got slides.
