Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're going to do like a review of basics.
