Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of review for all of us, so we're all on the same page, and, uh, especially
