Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness sakes alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gracious me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is that?
