Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that certainly is an interesting looking slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I could see it, it would help a lot.
