Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how all this work started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We started to count.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We discovered how to tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
