Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Any time somebody gets on from Washington or some country and pontificates, Susan and
