Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to review all so quickly how to tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody like to know how to tell truth from falsehood?
