Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see if they're telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people do want us to show them how to tell truth from falsehood.
